Class EntitySqlDaoWrapperFactory<InitialSqlDao extends EntitySqlDao>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ning.billing.util.entity.dao.EntitySqlDaoWrapperFactory<InitialSqlDao>
  • Type Parameters:
    InitialSqlDao - EntitySqlDao type to create

    public class EntitySqlDaoWrapperFactory<InitialSqlDao extends EntitySqlDao>
extends Object
    Factory to create wrapped EntitySqlDao objects. During a transaction, make sure to create other EntitySqlDao objects via the #become call.
    See Also:
    EntitySqlDaoWrapperInvocationHandler
